  "text": "Cells were seeded in 96-well plates with 2.5 × 10 3 cells in 100 L medium per well overnight before treatment with increasing concentrations of 2ME. Metabolic activity was assayed after incubation with 2ME for 72 h, using Alamar Blue reagent according to the manufacturer's protocol (Invitrogen, Carlsbad, CA, USA) [CITATION_1] .",
